data.description: Check out the 3D TOUR! This stunning home has just been renovated! Featuring brand new paint, new floors, new fixtures, new granite countertops. A sleek and stylish kitchen with plenty of storage space. The master bedroom features large closets and a luxurious bathroom with a garden tub. Secondary bedrooms have plenty of room for study, sleep, and storage. On cold nights, cozy up to the beautiful fireplace in the living room. The yard is perfect for pets to run around and explore. The covered patio in the back is ideal for coffee in the morning or spending time with family and friends.
